caption.p: Venn-diagram of the MEGs expressed in ascending and descending orders for the seeds of two cultivars ZS11 and ZY821. (ZS11_Inc: Ascendings MEGs for ZS11; ZS11_Dec: Descending MEGs for ZS11; ZY821_Inc: Ascendings MEGs for ZY821; ZY821_Dec: Descending MEGs for ZY821) (visualised with http://bioinformatics.psb.ugent.be/webtools/Venn/).
